{"lastModified":1774621737505,"uri":"c::18231584005::vessel::d5cc7704-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor","Power Catamaran"],"description":"Base / Home Port: Athens/Mykonos, Greece\nOperating Area: Greece\n\nIntroducing the Fountaine Pajot MY44 Endless Beauty – the pinnacle of power catamaran excellence.\nThis exceptional vessel seamlessly blends innovative design, remarkable performance, and luxurious comfort. With spacious interiors, fuel efficiency, and a focus on natural light, the MY44 offers an unforgettable cruising experience.\n\nExplore the seas with ease, and relish the outdoor spaces, including a panoramic flybridge and expansive decks. Discover the MY44 Endless Beauty, where power meets elegance.","blueprint":{"name":"ENDLESS BEAUTY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7704-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::qFMmPlUOV.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7704-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6a4a1b60-c9b1-11ee-967b-252c4f910e04.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7704-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6a4adeb0-c9b1-11ee-967b-252c4f910e04.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7704-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6a4b2cd0-c9b1-11ee-967b-252c4f910e04.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7704-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6a4c8c60-c9b1-11ee-967b-252c4f910e04.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7704-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6a4e6120-c9b1-11ee-967b-252c4f910e04.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7704-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6a4e3a10-c9b1-11ee-967b-252c4f910e04.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7704-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6a4b7af0-c9b1-11ee-967b-252c4f910e04.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7704-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6a4dc4e0-c9b1-11ee-967b-252c4f910e04.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::